text:
Aur bhai sharma ji ke ldke, kaisi chl rhi hai jindagi.  Hamare vote khaae hai tune koi wada poora nhi kiya . Teri publicity bhi maine hi ki thi sbse jyada :) , election ke time. Tere acche din bhi kbhi nhi aaye .Tujhe poori wing ne apnaya tha ye kbhi mt bhhoolna. 
Bhai thodi si coding skills mujhe bhi dede . Jb tu kisi mst company mein jaaega to mujhe bhi apne saath rkh liyo. I think teeri sbse badi khoobi hai ki Tu hr cheez try krta hai.  Ye to kehna padega ki tune HEC mein sbse jyada kaam kiya. Bhai jb agli baar milenge to pkka mast si movie dekhne jaaenge. Paise tu dega aur party bhi. Kaash mai campus aa pata but koi nhi milte rhenge. all the best for CISCO.  Aage bhi chaapte rehna. Stay in touch.
author: Vishesh  Kaushik

text:
Gamer, Anime Lover, Foodie, Bulla ktwalo, cuber,  bs pdhne ko mt bolo. Mastmaula aadmi. 
Bhai tune mujhe aaj tk ek bhi party nhi di. First year mein mila tha bhai ke roop mein. Afsosjanak baat thi mere liye. campus aate hi manhusiyat. Unpadh ne sir pe daali girwali thi. PE mein reh gya btao kaisa aadmi hai.  Clash of clans mein bhi haara tha mujhse. Sharam kr. Hit Spray wali fight mein bhi haara the tu aur nishchay mujhse. 

Boore time pe help krne ke liye thanks bhai. Tu hamesha motivate krta tha kisiko bhi jo tension mein rehta tha wing mein. Gussa km kiya kr nhi to mujhse to pit hi jaaega. Mujhe gamer banane ke liye thanks bhai. Autocad bhi tujhse hi seekha tha. Kaash first year dobara zee paate. All the best bhai aage ki life ke liye. milte rhenge.
author: Vishesh  Kaushik

text:

text:
Kya likhu tumhare baare mein yehi soch rha tha. Tumhara wo mst dance performance jiska video bhi hai mere paas. Bhai exam ke last din pdhkr chaapna koi tumse seekhe. Aur kisi bhi baat pr beemar pdna ya chot khana bhi koi tumse seekhe.  CSK ko andha hokr pyaar dena bnd krdo ab, us team ka kuch nhi ho skta. Yaad hai "MAINE DIYA GAALI". Soumya ke memoir mein nhi likhna bhool gya. Diwali yaad hai na jb A105 ko humne dhua dhua kiya tha. Isliye thoda drke rha kro.
Ye btao ki kaisi chl rhi Zomato mein delivery boy ki zindagi. Covid mein kaafi mushkil ho rha hoga.
Jokes Apart, Ek acha dost bnne ke liye thanks bhai .  aise hi chaapte rho. All the best for your future endeavour and keep up the good work.

text:
"DHOKEBAAZ HAI TU RE"
Pdhne wale vyakti SRD chup chaap is upar wali line ko maanle. Itni ldkiyon ko dhoka diya. CSE,EE,ME,Adobe  sbko dhoka diya.  Bilkul apni team CSK pe gaya hai wo IPL fix kr rhi hai aur ye IIT mein sbko dhoka de rha hai. TA mein bhi fraud maarta tha. Thoda kaam krta to hum muh dikhane layak to rehte TA ke project mein. PRERNA ka register to yaad hai.

Jokes Apart, SRD yaar tum jaisa difficult situation ko face krne wala bnda nhi dekha. Calm and composed. Aur chaapne mein bhi sbse aage.Kuch number to choddo prof ke liye jise wo kaat ske. Leadership skills ke to kya kehne. 
All the best for all of your future endeavour.   Bn jaaoge jo tum bnna chahte ho, i am sure about it.
author: Vishesh  Kaushik

text:
Abe kitna ladega. har baat pe ladai aur hmesha mai hi sorry bolta tha. Aur kaisi chl rhi hai zindagi. Bhai IITK mein sbse acha time bhi tumhare saath hi share kiya maine.  bhai tumhe pareshaan krne mein bda maja aata tha. " AE AANA ". preena samuel ko regrading request kyun ki thi?  Photography bekaar hai teri but meri ek photo kheech dena linkedin ke liye. Udgosh mein gilli danda bhi rkhwalete kyunki doosre sports koi dekhne to aata nhi tha. Avengers ke stickers mein bhi tumne ghaplebaazi ki thi.  Phone mein hr doosri chat mein ladki hai teri, kuch to sharam kr.  Modiji ache hai unhe suport kr kyunki agli baar modi sarkaar to hai hi mere paas hr debate se bachne ke liye. Gaane mt gaaya kr bhai please. Lyrics ka kuch pta bhi rehta hai tujhe. Bhai kbhi to MT mein kudh se paise khrch kiye hote tune samosa pe. Humesha mere chillar khrch hote the. Bob marley se bekaar pasand aur koi nhi hai. Daroo, drugs , sootta chhhode. Vipul ne tere ghr ko dhua dhua kiya tha yaad hai na. Sports mein zero hai tu. Tujhe bahut kuch seekhna hai mujhse abhi.
Mathisys mein andha paisa kmate kmate hume bhool mt jaana. Thanks bhai ek bahut acha dost bnne ke liye. Humesha help ki tune yaar. Milte rhenge .Stay in touch. All the best for future endeavour.
author: Vishesh  Kaushik

text:
Aur bhai Yatin kaise ho. 
Mai ye poora memoir hindi mein likhunga nhi to tum mere memoir mein meri english ki galtiyaan ginane beth jaaoge. Aaj bhi yaad hai TA101 mein tushank and loki tumhe lock krke chle gye the.
Tum itne sareef kyun ho. Duniya badi harami hai wo tumhare standards ke bahut neeche hai. Mai apni poori wing ki taraf se maafi maangta hu jitno ne bhi tumhe pareshaan kiya particularly karan .
Chaapu aadmi Wing mein akele tumhara DS mein A tha.  
Tumse maine kuch baatein seekhi jaise ki tum Kaafi clearly apna stand explain krte ho kisi bhi cheez pe, kisi bhi majaak ko seriously nhi lete (bus itni hi hai :)). Humesha aise hi rehna and stay in touch buddy. All the very best for the future.
